OL,3,CRoad closed in both directions due to
OL,4,Coverturned lorry
OL,6,FPart of the A69 in Cumbria has been
OL,7,Fclosed in both directions due to an
OL,8,Foverturned lorry.
OL,10,FThe incident happened at Warwick
OL,11,FBridge near Carlisle and the road
OL,12,Fbetween Great Corby Road and the B6263
OL,13,FWetheral Turning is closed tonight.
OL,15,FWitnesses reported police officers and
OL,16,Fthe fire brigade at the scene at
OL,17,Faround 7pm on Tuesday (2 June).
OL,19,FThe area is close to where another
OL,20,Florry crashed through the garden of a
OL,21,Fhouse in the village three weeks ago.
